1
00:00:05,000 --> 00:00:09,872
I walk the house with just one in

2
00:00:10,022 --> 00:00:14,893
The other sleeps in its plastic bin

3
00:00:15,043 --> 00:00:19,915
Left ear takes the morning shift

4
00:00:20,065 --> 00:00:24,937
Right comes in when spirits lift

5
00:00:25,087 --> 00:00:29,958
With one AirPod, I can go all night long

6
00:00:30,108 --> 00:00:34,980
Swapping sides like nothing’s wrong

7
00:00:35,130 --> 00:00:40,002
Mono sound, a half-full song

8
00:00:40,152 --> 00:00:45,023
But the vibe rolls steady, all night long

9
00:00:45,173 --> 00:00:50,045
No surround, no perfect bass

10
00:00:50,195 --> 00:00:55,067
But I stay in the rhythm race

11
00:00:55,217 --> 00:01:00,088
Don’t need both to feel the beat

12
00:01:00,238 --> 00:01:05,110
One’s enough to move my feet

13
00:01:05,260 --> 00:01:10,132
With one AirPod, I can go all night long

14
00:01:10,282 --> 00:01:15,153
Keep one charging while I hum along

15
00:01:15,303 --> 00:01:20,175
Not stereo, not crystal-clear

16
00:01:20,325 --> 00:01:25,197
But I’ve got sound in at least one ear

17
00:01:25,347 --> 00:01:30,218
Battery low? That’s not my fate

18
00:01:30,368 --> 00:01:35,240
I alternate and circulate

19
00:01:35,390 --> 00:01:40,262
It’s not ideal, but it’s my way

20
00:01:40,412 --> 00:01:45,283
To keep the music night and day

21
00:01:45,433 --> 00:01:50,305
With one AirPod, I can go all night long

22
00:01:50,455 --> 00:01:55,327
It’s not loud, but the will is strong

23
00:01:55,477 --> 00:02:00,348
One side silent, one side plays—

24
00:02:00,498 --> 00:02:05,370
And that’s how I stretch out all my days
